---
title: Tex-Mex Steak Over Zesty Rice plus Pico de Gallo & Red Pepper-Lime Crema
description: Steak and rice is always a winning combination—especially when you spice it all up with bold Tex-Mex flavors and fresh lime juice. You’ll pile tender spiced steak and onion atop zesty lime rice. Drizzle your bowls with tangy red pepper-lime crema and finish with homemade pico de gallo for added brightness and voila! Dinner is served.
